channel.title: Class8 compile error
channel.description:
Even if I leave Class8.class unedited then decompile, I get this error when I compile:
[code]Class8.java:26: illegal start of expression if(i >= 10500) goto _L2; else goto _L1 ^ Class8.java:26: not a statement if(i >= 10500) goto _L2; else goto _L1 ^ Class8.java:26: 'else' without 'if' if(i >= 10500) goto _L2; else goto _L1 ^ Class8.java:26: illegal start of expression if(i >= 10500) goto _L2; else goto _L1 ^ Class8.java:26: ';' expected if(i >= 10500) goto _L2; else goto _L1 ^ Class8.java:28: not a statement Class8 class8; ^ Class8.java:28: ';' expected Class8 class8; ^ Class8.java:28: not a statement Class8 class8; ^ Class8.java:46: not a statement ioexception1; ^ Class8.java:57: not a statement exception; ^ Class8.java:66: illegal start of expression goto _L3 ^ Class8.java:67: ';' expected _L2: ^ 12 errors Press any key to continue . . . [/code]
Is there any way to fix this?
